5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"}],"bridge_alerts":[],"claim_harness":"claude-code_2-1-215_agent","claim_remote_session":null,"claimed_session":"5e1736fd-6a46-425f-96e3-3460f9fcb4f7","comments":[],"created_at":1783981877882086001,"creation_channel":"unknown","deps":[{"link_uuid":"60fbe346-3df6-46dc-aded-f74c56a7bf0c","relation":"discovered_from","target_id":"ce0e-f618-a2a4-4ee4"}],"description":"## Reproduction Steps\n\nDiscovered while validating epic ce0e (xdist parallelization). The live-Jira\nreconciler E2E `test_delete_permission_probe` flakes on Jira's search-index\neventual consistency when the *whole* live group runs (it self-skips in CI, so\nthis only bites a local live run with creds).\n\n- `pytest tests/integration/test_reconcile_live_e2e.py` (all 12, SERIAL, no xdist)\n  → `test_delete_permission_probe` FAILS: `AssertionError: created issue REB-NNNN\n  never became index-visible` (observed REB-1105 and REB-1107 on two runs).\n- `pytest \"…::test_delete_permission_probe\"` in ISOLATION (serial) → PASSES.\n\nSo the failure is load/timing dependent (many live tests hammering the shared\ntest project's index in one run outrun the test's index-visibility poll timeout),\nNOT caused by xdist — it reproduces with `-n0`. Independent of epic ce0e's change.\n\n## Expected vs Actual\n\n- Expected: the index-visibility wait polls long enough (or backs off) to absorb\n  Jira's eventual-consistency lag even when the full live group has just created\n  many issues.\n- Actual: the fixed poll budget in the visibility helper (`test_reconcile_live_e2e.py:347`)\n  times out under group load and the test fails.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] The index-visibility wait in `tests/integration/test_reconcile_live_e2e.py`\n  is made robust to group-load lag (e.g. longer/adaptive backoff, or a\n  create→visible retry helper) so the full live group passes reliably.\n- [ ] `pytest tests/integration/test_reconcile_live_e2e.py` (all 12, serial) passes\n  repeatedly against the live test project (no `never became index-visible`).\n- [ ] No change to CI behavior (these tests still self-skip without live creds).","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[],"parent_id":null,"parent_status_uuid":"90416de9-4316-4eaf-82ff-f1e01058c79a","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"d30c-f491-395f-432e","ticket_type":"bug","title":"Live reconciler E2E test_delete_permission_probe flakes on Jira index-visibility under live-group load","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["784587a8-c423-451d-a3ad-64fe2b74cb3c","60fbe346-3df6-46dc-aded-f74c56a7bf0c","90416de9-4316-4eaf-82ff-f1e01058c79a","8d487af6-f3b1-4982-a572-e98d3e41add1","2f83e4d7-059b-4944-aba3-e6e9cff8faa8"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784488213629688403,"uuid":"ad0959b2-6176-4eae-bbff-a1d2893241a3"}